{"url": "https://ew.com/tv/2017/09/29/american-idol-luke-bryan-lionel-richie-judges/", "text": "And just like that, the judges table is full.\n\nABC\u2019s American Idol reboot has added Lionel Richie and country singer Luke Bryan as its second and third judges, Fox announced Friday. The pair join Katy Perry just as auditions are getting underway.\n\n\u201cI am very excited to be joining Katy, Luke, and Ryan on American Idol,\u201d Richie, who has sold more than 100 million albums worldwide and won four Grammys, said in a statement. \u201cAs a singer, songwriter, and producer, I feel I can bring a great deal of experience to the table. It\u2019s going to be so much fun!\u201d\n\n\u201cI\u2019m excited at the chance to help some deserving artists reach their dreams,\u201d said Bryan, whose last three releases all debuted at the top of Billboard\u2019s Top Country Albums chart. \u201cTo be in a position in my career to help facilitate this along with the other judges is just a complete honor. It\u2019s gonna be a blast!\u201d\n\nPerry and host Ryan Seacrest shared their excitement on Twitter.\n\nPerry, Richie, and Bryan will make their first appearance as a trio on Good Morning America on Oct. 4.\n\nABC announced in May that it was reviving the long-running Fox reality series, a little more than a year after the show went off the air. Seacrest will also be returning when the new season debuts next year.", "images": ["https://ew.com/thmb/ZDH93SMwYWb25cUxG6Aw1L8c7uE=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/adrianne-curry-tyra-banks-110325-f7189a016cf24a489d7801f9473ad007.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/bzx2ihGFEaEFGvdZR8QDLhMEG18=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Isla-Fisher-The-Kelly-Clarkson-Show-110725-1-5759d8c7995b4f268fef35ee30e80044.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/-ivDnUSajL4K0kJbIidzxPPC14U=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/ariana-grande-AMERICAN-HORROR-STORY-HOTEL-Evan-Peters-AMERICAN-HORROR-STORY-Sarah-Paulson-110525-03f4062fe1cf4ba2b0069fca7f0f0363.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/CZnm21SNYBYdPch0gJHc6Cs3pk0=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Randy-Madden-110425-63e0484e2a8545c69986482763639f1b.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/lLdGDBc2n__4WY4s7zJ0AQO_XIw=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/split2-2000-a190fead34484162af292ece771975b9.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/3dcmGq8m9pLNXwYlI5brh0_kta4=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Ozzy-Osbourne-and-Sharon-Osbourne-Roger-Waters-111325-dd072efad0414740a45d08ed635ee2d6.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/gIspAPLpIts1ggieMmCkf089Hxw=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Gwen-Stefani-Dolly-Parton-Jennifer-Lopez-101525-6a26296da2294aeb84aa1e634aa293b1.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/yGEg8eU7BS_RsIp2ypIXcSj6Raw=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/flavor-flav-304-110425-308-110425-32da8a3cce834f11a000a64f616205fd.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/Vjh9_ZdJ6Wq02cFFtPSg7M6njS0=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/joshua-allen-83rd-Annual-Hollywood-Christmas-Parade-2014-111225-b41e4f04497d4e12bd081e7bb34a7656.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/a9z6rAK_eFGxvcseGf9IxnjadE4=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/dylan-efron-zac-efron-dwts-111925-1-1665af41eff140859db3daddd5d088e8.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/33raakqvrXBoKxo1xPa6BBVX_Qo=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/AmericanIdolFinale-051925-02-5b4e326d4682481ab1163cf8c118786f.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/FT0S5qfFJwczfiYRJj44M7H3WUQ=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/American-Idol-judges-082525-bf88b00515544395a8ac6f9cd2b475c2.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/-7IWA_G_WdyGW6UhfvqolxJWT5Q=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Marissa-Bode-355-110625-8d41b1ff37704143965afb0b302282d0.jpg", "https://ew.com/thmb/VzRrj8NdutSKJvw9tj6reX2bebQ=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/tyra-b